INSERT INTO public.job VALUES (1154, 'https://www.computrabajo.com.uy/ofertas-de-trabajo/oferta-de-trabajo-de-business-development-analyst-en-salto-8A901ABF7E7FDB9661373E686DCF3405', 'Business Development Analyst', 'remote', 'notspecified', 'other', NULL, NULL, 'BairesDev is proud to be one of the fastest-growing companies in Latin America and a welcoming, highly rated employer (Glassdoor Employee Score: 4.3). With more than 1,300 employees in 27 countries and world-class clients from start-ups to Fortune 500 companies, we’re only as strong as the multicultural teams at the heart of our business. BairesDev runs on talent. To consistently deliver the highest quality solutions to our clients, we only hire the Top 1% of IT Talent and nurture their professional growth on exciting projects for companies like Google, Pinterest, and Udemy. We are looking for a Business Development Analyst to join our Sales team. We are looking for proactive, dynamic people and team players, with great organizational capacity, accustomed to handle multiple tasks and with marked attention to details. It is an excellent opportunity for those professionals looking to develop in one of the fastest growing companies in the industry!Main Activities:- Execute Business Development initiatives.- Interact/manage potential business providers/partners.- Generate and improve email templates.- Manage business providers (Sales Agents who introduce us to potential clients).- Interface with Sales Ops area when we are introduced to a potential client.- Cold/Warm call potential providers/partners.- Execute and improve internal processes. What are we looking for: - Commercial background.- At least 5 years of total experience.- Prospecting (Desirable).- Lead Generation (Desirable). - Sales in the SW industry (Desirable).- Advanced English level.Perks:- Excellent compensation plan, well above the market average.- Possibility of remote work and flexible schedules.- Training plans.- Extensive possibilities for growth and professional development thanks to our mentoring system.If you are interested in being part of a team composed of the best professionals and working 100% goal-oriented in an innovative environment, but with the structure and resources of a multinational market leader, do not hesitate to apply!', 178, 7, true, '2020-11-18 19:27:06.624823');
INSERT INTO public.job VALUES (1155, 'https://www.computrabajo.com.uy/ofertas-de-trabajo/oferta-de-trabajo-de-vendedor-viajante-para-el-litoral-con-vehiculo-propio-para-importante-empresa-de-aberturas-en-aluminio-en-paysandu-70672C29ED9A5F0861373E686DCF3405', 'Vendedor viajante para el litoral con vehículo propio', 'Paysandu, Paysandú', 'fulltime', 'undefined', NULL, NULL, 'Buscamos:Nos encontramos en la búsqueda de personas con bachillerato completo y experiencia previa en ventas en el litoral. Será requisito excluyente contar con conocimientos en productos de barraca y/o ferretería y poseer vehículo propio.Desafíos:La persona seleccionada se encargará de viajar por el interior del país ofreciendo los artículos que vende la empresa a posibles clientes. Manejará su propia cartera de clientes y tendrá como objetivo expandirla.Propuesta:Es una excelente oportunidad para integrarse de forma permanente a una reconocida empresa nacional que ofrece muy buen ambiente laboral y un nivel de remuneración acorde a las responsabilidades.', 176, 7, true, '2020-11-18 19:27:06.702652');
